file_content.text: Shutdown order received. All walker production suspended.
Do my words reach you? We have made this Guardian Hold Six our shell.
We've succeeded, thanks to your heroic action outside.
You've done well.
Are you okay?
The enemy's furnace tested us. Some are broken, others whole.
I'm still looking for Aelan Kalder. Be wary of him.
Have you seen the traitor?
But the wound still runs red.
This Empire paced our footsteps here, Sky Hunter. They make machines their snarling dogs. We are raw and torn.
This Empire paced our footsteps here, Ember Fist. They make machines their snarling dogs. We are raw and torn.
This Empire paced our footsteps here, Silent Teeth. They make machines their snarling dogs. We are raw and torn.
Don't engage yet, hold back until I get there.
Wait for me.
Hold the line a little longer, I'll be there soon.
Be strong, I'm coming.
Your words are water and light.
If you survived the walkers, a few Imperial soldiers shouldn't stop you.
Can't you handle them alone?
We are bloody and twisting, so that you are whole. We need you.
Please walk swiftly.
Jedi, do you read? Our droids have made it inside Guardian Hold Six.
The production is shut off. No more walkers.
Our mission is complete.
Don't celebrate yet.
How many droids did we lose, Tai?
Casualties?
I haven't seen Aelan Kalder anywhere. Keep the droids' guard up.
No sign of the traitor yet.
Jedi, the battle's not over.
The droids report one of the Imperial walker crews followed them and activated hostile units on the factory floor.
Our droids are having a tough time. Anything you can do?
Alert the droids that friendly forces are coming.
Tell them I'm coming.
I'll handle this.
Good, good, I can't send any more in time.
So we lose a few units. It's not as if people are dying.
They're only droids.
Balmorran sweat built those droids, to defend Corellia. We need every one we can salvage.
Just come as fast as you can.
We must speak. Commandos have destroyed walkers. They shelter inside Guardian Hold Six.
With walker production shut down, your commandos should be okay.
So they're safe.
They are not.
Gaden-Ko, how many dead or injured?
Casualties?
Many. More to come.
Tell any who are unharmed or walking wounded to search for Aelan Kalder.
We have a traitor to find.
They cannot.
Imperial survivors followed, activating factory droids. Commandos need you now.
Give your commandos any tactical intuition you have, I'll be there.
Advise them until I arrive.
I'm coming.
My priority must be tracking down this Child of the Emperor, wherever he is.
But I have a traitor to find.
Commandos need you. Now. Or all die.
Be quick.
